comments: Gafford (WAS) is already in Watanabe's (BKN) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Watanabe (BKN) legally contests Kispert's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in Wright's (WAS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Wright (WAS) makes contact with Thomas' (BKN) left elbow as he is starting his upward shooting motion, and the contact affects his jump shot.
Mills (BKN) brings his hand towards Morris' (WAS) side and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Morris (WAS) brings his off-arm towards Mills' (BKN) forearm/hand and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Mills (BKN) applies his left hand to Morris' (WAS) side and immediately removes his hand as Morris begins his upward shooting motion.
Avdija (WAS) and Sumner (BKN) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Avdija (WAS) legally contests Mills' (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Kispert (WAS) firms up over his right leg and absorbs the contact from Mills (BKN) during the pick.
Thomas (BKN) and Gafford (WAS) briefly grasps each other's arms and marginal contact occurs as they disengage following the pick.
Thomas (BKN) moves into Morris (WAS) and initiates body to body contact that affects Morris' shot attempt.
Thomas (BKN) receives the ball on his right foot and takes more than two steps after his gather.
Wright (WAS) legally contests Thomas' (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Claxton (BKN) and Gafford (WAS) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Mills (BKN) legally contests Morris' (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Sumner (BKN) brings his arms out towards Nunn (WAS) and marginal contact occurs as Sumner releases away to receive the pass.
Avdija (WAS) turns into Thomas' (BKN) body and initiates contact prior to Thomas' gather.

After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined the ruling on the court (defensive goaltending) would stand.  Gafford (WAS) touches the ball after it reaches it apex and begins its downward flight with a chance to score.
Gafford (WAS) firms up on his right leg and he absorbs the contact from Watanbe (BKN) during the screen.
Gafford (WAS) and Claxton (BKN) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Watanabe (BKN) legally contests Kispert's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Sumner (BKN) and Gafford (WAS) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as Gafford secures the rebound.
Thomas (BKN) moves forward into Morris' (WAS) space and initiates lower body contact that affects Morris' SQBR.
O'Neale (BKN) and Avdija (WAS) briefly engage and disengage during rbeounding.
Avdija (WAS) loses control of the ball on his own prior to any contact from Sumner (BKN).
Thomas (BKN) leaves his feet to pass and he releases the ball before he returns to the floor.
Wright (WAS) brings his hands towards Thomas (BKN) and marginal contact occurs as Thomas passes the ball.
